data.eml:eml: Competing Taxonomies: Reexamination of the female­based genera of Brachycistidinae (Hymenoptera: Tiphiidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Kimsey, Lynn S. (2006): Competing Taxonomies: Reexamination of the female­based genera of Brachycistidinae (Hymenoptera: Tiphiidae). Zootaxa 1211: 21-34, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.172480
